blog.name: fonsecashow
blog.title: Fonseca Show
blog.description:
Comedic performer, radio personality,Voice Artist Fonseca has made an indelible mark in the entertainment world with his captivating enthusiasm and quick-witted style. His familiar voice and multitude of characters have become a mainstay of the American psyche and have even extended into Beijing, China voicing cartoons for children’s networks.

radioimaging

Fonseca became the hottest property in radio when he began hosting the top rated morning radio show in Ventura, CA on B95.1 in July of 2002. In a short time, he turned B95.1 into the #1 rated station in Southern California. In April 2007 partnering with Cumulus Media and rocketed to the top with CBS radio.

His latest ventures reflect his expansion into the digital realm, expanding distribution of his own abundant entertainment content, as well as launching many online digital channels at Fonsecashow.com

tv2In television, Fonseca hosted Average Joe, TV shows How I Met Your Mother, Drew Carey Show, Blind Date, and his voice has been enjoyed on numerous animated features, including House Of Mouse and G.I. Joe.

While his ingrained sense of the absurd and his fervent love of comedy have earned him top ratings in every city in which he has performed, Fonseca also has become a consummate businessman and entrepreneur. He is the founder/partner of Fonseca Imaging, which is now working with 13 stations in the United States..

Fonseca graduated from San Francisco State University with a bachelor’s degree in Radio, TV and Motion Pictures. Active in Young Life, an organization committed to helping youth in their formative years, Fonseca also is a proud participant in the Boy Scouts Of America, having earned the rank of Eagle Scout himself at age 18.

Currently Fonseca is on air at KKIQ, KKDV, SIRIUS RADIO, and Hosting the San Francisco Bulls

Professional Hockey Team. While being heard in Tampa Bay, Idaho, Arkansaw…Too
